e Twilight Sea armor quests fall between Temple of Ro quests and Hate/Fear armor in terms of quality.  The Ranger BP has 17 AC, for example, and the melee bracers seem to range between 10 and 12 AC.  These definitely aren't &quot;epic&quot; quests in any form of the word... unless you consider the epic amount of time you'll need to spend to get the quest pieces, which are annoyingly rare. <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=12621">Baron Aledar Boomcaster</a><br>Sorcerer of <a href="http://www.reconstructed.nu/">Reconstructed</a>, E'ci<br><img src="http://www.seas.upenn.edu/~bwa/kerasig.jpg"></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/urombusmindspire.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Rombus Mindspire</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle><table width=111><tr><td style=filter:glow(color=#6633FF strength=1);font-family:arial;font-weight;bold;font-size:'1pt' nowrap><font size=1 color=#FFFFFF face=Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif>Forum Sorcerer</font></td></tr></table><table width=111><tr><td style=filter:glow(color=#6633FF strength=1);font-family:arial;font-weight;bold;font-size:'1pt' nowrap><font size=1 color=#FFFFFF face=Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif>NOT Rhombus!</font></td></tr></table></span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(1/2/02 5:08:08 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.tritonguild.com/rombus/sidepic.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: bah. crits with items?</span><hr size=1> Like I said in another thread.. my personal bet is that Vex Thal is an uber quest zone simular to Plane of Sky with Epic Items as rewards for quest completion.  Personally I would love to see another zone simular to PoS. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ueelyen.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Eelyen</A>